{"tid":587724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一首以前聽唔明 大個突然明左嘅歌","createTime":"2018-03-10T15:46:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T07:14:53.000Z","uid":172388,"like":14,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ced37fd385aa2f2ab3e572a9c740557985cb7df9","tid":587724,"uid":172388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:46:47.000Z","msg":"農夫嘅偉大航道 以前真係當佢9up<br />\n但最近開始出嚟做嘢 再聽返又唔同感覺 聽到眼濕濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">//細路哥細細個仲細得幾多年<br />\n唔好俾你嘅童年淨係充滿考試同測驗<br />\n望下個天 咁好天 去下海邊<br />\n因為到你大個就會忘記乜嘢係大自然<br />\n<br />\n做學生要爭取時間玩<br />\n有幾多功課做都好閒 唔駛喊<br />\n當你正式上班 先知道乜嘢叫慘<br />\n原來做功課好簡單 做人好難<br />\n<br />\n唔好怪你學校好似好煩個幾個先生<br />\n因為冇一個先生係可以煩得過你老闆<br />\n唔好介意 記缺點只係小事<br />\n操行分就係玩緊迷你版嘅辦公室政治//</span>"},{"pid":"dacf5de10b1ab084f2a5deac7497a484a8df029a","tid":587724,"uid":3548,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔先聽農夫 認真"},{"pid":"1db1cb0842b07e2c8ffd3e596a1e74e3f81d8848","tid":587724,"uid":55,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:51:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"147c4a5697984b92da43dffbce21d30d7eef240e","tid":587724,"uid":125434,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:52:32.000Z","msg":"一路向北<br />\n一路傷悲"},{"pid":"33fb2b086999bd96fdd07ebd63fb70d0fff5926d","tid":587724,"uid":172388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dacf5de10b1ab084f2a5deac7497a484a8df029a","tid":587724,"uid":3548,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"細蚊仔先聽農夫 認真"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T15:54:07.000Z","msg":"介紹下大人聽既歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6cb99d168ea62762b77f118ad6eb96ca5181954","tid":587724,"uid":126651,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"陳奕迅 十年<br />\n十年前唔明 <br />\n十年後 我心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/n